signatures.text: inline fun CharSequence.filterIndexed( predicate: (index: Int, Char) -> Boolean): CharSequence
signatures.desc: Returns a char sequence containing only those characters from the original char sequence that match the given predicate.

signatures.text: inline fun String.filterIndexed( predicate: (index: Int, Char) -> Boolean): String
